    <string name="ai_analysis_standard">Analysis Standard</string>
    <string name="ai_standard_intro">The AI analysis is based on established psychological frameworks, primarily Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT). Here\'s what the analysis covers:</string>
    <string name="ai_standard_framework_title">📋 Analysis Framework</string>
    <string name="ai_standard_framework_desc">CBT (Cognitive Behavioral Therapy) focuses on the relationship between thoughts, emotions, and behaviors. The AI identifies recurring patterns in your diary entries and provides insights grounded in this evidence-based approach.</string>
    <string name="ai_standard_dimensions_title">📊 Analysis Dimensions</string>
    <string name="ai_standard_dimensions_desc">• Overall Mood — Summarizes your predominant emotional state\n• Key Themes — Recurring topics and concerns in your life\n• Emotional Patterns — How your emotions typically unfold\n• Cognitive Distortions — Unhelpful thinking patterns (see below)\n• Suggestions — Practical steps based on CBT principles\n• Positive Highlights — Strengths and positive aspects noticed</string>
    <string name="ai_standard_distortions_title">⚠️ Cognitive Distortions Monitored</string>
    <string name="ai_standard_distortions_desc">• Catastrophizing — Assuming the worst will happen\n• Black-and-White Thinking — Seeing things as all good or all bad\n• Overgeneralization — Drawing broad conclusions from a single event\n• Personalization — Taking excessive responsibility for external events\n• Should-Statements — Rigid rules about how things "should" be\n• Emotional Reasoning — Assuming feelings reflect reality\n• Labeling — Assigning global negative labels to self or others\n• Mind Reading — Assuming you know what others think</string>
    <string name="ai_standard_trend_title">📈 Mood Trend Indicators</string>
    <string name="ai_standard_trend_desc">• Improving — Positive shift in emotional state over the period\n• Stable — Consistent emotional state\n• Declining — Signs of increasing distress or negative patterns\n\nRisk Warning: When the AI detects signs of severe distress (self-harm, suicidal ideation), a prominent warning will be displayed.</string>
